<h1>重要资源</h1>
<ul>
<li>TuyaOpen 代码仓库：<a href="https://github.com/tuya/TuyaOpen" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
<li>TuyaOpen 文档官网：<a href="https://tuyaopen.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">文档</a></li>
